⚡【Widely Used DP to HDMI】Our DP to HDMI Cable is perfectly compatible with laptops (HP ProBook EliteBook, Lenovo ThinkPad), desktops (HP, Dell optiplex/Precision/xps, Lenovo), graphics card (AMD, NVIDIA), and more devices with display ports. Provides life like and fluent frames to your large display screen, giving you a realistic 3D screen experience. HDCP compliant for stream media.

⚡【4K UHD Resolution/Audio & Video Sync Transmission】DisplayPort to HDMI Cable 10ft can supports max 4K@30Hz resolution, (Backward supports 2K@120Hz/1080P@120Hz), and flawless audio pass-thru for uncompressed digital 7.1, 5.1 or 2 channels. Our DisplayPort to HDMI 4K is suitable for extended or mirrored mode, supports both high-definition audio and video pass through from your computer to an HDMI input, ensures smooth, life-like frames and crystal-clear sound for video streaming or gaming.

⚡【High Quality Material & Signal Transmission】 Displayport Cable to HDMI with multi-layer shielding design, sturdy and easy heat dissipation aluminum housing, bend-resistant nylon braided wire (20,000+ times bending test) and 24K gold-plated one-piece connector reduces signal interference, video and audio failure, artifacts and audio and video synchronization problems, without complicated installation and drivers, enough to transmit high quality and stable video and audio signals.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on November 15, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Cleans up the Build
reviews.reviewText: These cords do the job or replacing hdmi cables with adapters attached. The thing I like is how all the ports on graphics cards can be used with these cords and they look nice too. I have had to even whittle away at hdmi cable heads to get them to fit onto graphics cards with other connectors present. The other think I like is that this does not have those annoying princers which grasp onto the graphic card interior. It is easy to pull these on and off the card. Overall, these cords are useful for having hdmi monitors attached to a graphics card with DP ports.

Issues in the past with cables that are so heavy they warp the hdmi connector on the cable or the device. This cable is not like that it is flat and light, yet well made. Does not weigh down the connector, also ribbon cable does not get tangled like cables normally do.
